      About

      Description

      Blackpink is a South Korean girl group formed by YG Entertainment, consisting of members Jisoo, Jennie, Ros, and Lisa. Wikipedia
      Active from: 2016
      Genres: K-pop; EDM; hip hop; trap
      Record labels: YG Entertainment, Interscope Records, YGEX
      Awards: Seoul Music Awards Bonsang Awards, Golden Disc Award Song Division, MTV Video Music Award for the Best Song of the Summer, More

      Lisa
      Thai rapper
      Lalisa Manobal, known mononymously as Lisa, is a Thai rapper, singer and dancer based in South Korea. She is a member of the South Korean girl group Blackpink formed by YG Entertainment. Lisa made her solo debut with her single album Lalisa in September 2021. Wikipedia
